original: Åberg, Johan Olof Tage, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 24/6/07 i Sthlm av käll:-mäst. Johan A. o. Ellen Rehn. G. 36 m. Anna-Lisa Karlsson. — Stud:ex. i Örebro 27, Cand. med. dent. i Rostock 31, tysk tandläk. i Bonn 32, svensk tandlläk. 34. Prakt, i Trollhättan 37-46, egen prakt, i Mölndal sed. 46.
translated: Åberg, Johan Olof Tage, dentist, Gothenburg, b. 24/6/07 in Stockholm, son of moulder Johan A. and Ellen Rehn. Married for 36 years to Anna-Lisa Karlsson. — Completed secondary school in Örebro in 1927, obtained a degree in dental medicine in Rostock in 1931, practiced as a German dentist in Bonn in 1932, and became a Swedish dentist in 1934. Practiced dentistry in Trollhättan from 1937 to 1946, and has had his own practice in Mölndal since 1946.
